    "English": "A highly-advanced upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Pulse Engine</span>, vastly increasing <span class=\"name name-stellar\">interplanetary speed</span>.<br><br>Naturally occuring frameshift effects within the Pulse Engine are amplified by tritium-based resonators, increasing its maximum sub-light speed.",
